@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xhifsc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos((tmp * (v0 + 0.76 + v1 + 0.37)))
    tmp = (tmp * (tmp - (v2 + 0.46 / v0 + 0.88)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(v2) / v2)
    data[tid] = v0
